00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:26.160
Koristi se hitro pokažejo.

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:31.160
Z zdravo prehrano, manj stresa, več telovadbe in ljubezni

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.160
